Olawale Ajimotokan in Abuja President Muhammadu has approved the appointment of Dr (Mrs) Sakirat Oluwatoyin Madein as the substantive Accountant General of the Federation following the successful conduct of the selection process to fill the existing vacancy.  The Head of Civil Service of the Federation, Dr Folasade Yemi-Esan, said in a statement Friday that Madein’s appointment was with effect from Thursday, May 18, 2023. The statement said the new appointee is to resume immediately. Buhari Approves Appointment of Madein as Accountant General of Federation Olawale Ajimotokan in Abuja President Muhammadu has approved the appointment of Dr (Mrs) Sakirat Oluwatoyin Madein as the substantive Accountant General of the Federation following the successful conduct of the selection process to fill the existing vacancy.  The Head of Civil Service of the Federation, Dr Folasade Yemi-Esan, said in a statement Friday that Madein’s appointment was with effect from Thursday, May 18, 2023. The statement said the new appointee is to resume immediately.